: 443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have not been out of the country at all before, this will be my first time.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to get my passport just to go to this trip,\\\" graduate student Te'yanah Owens said.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Students will visit Marseille, Lyon and Paris to produce written, visual and digital stories.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999454798436815, \"rank\": 5.44994146981621e-05, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}, {\"begin\": 645, \"end\": 649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"score\": 0.9996914087450739, \"rank\": 0.00029864283437601853, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\"}, {\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996271186105, \"rank\": 3.7288149755628017e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am super grateful for Dean Bissell who's been able to bring this project to the Manship School, and having the opportunity to go is rally exciting,\\\" graduate student Marileah Niddrie said.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 734, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9729579839978478, \"rank\": 0.027317893176298607, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\":